{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/report-actions.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>There are several actions you can take on a report in your inbox. You can:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a comment</li>\n<li>Close a report</li>\n<li>Change the state</li>\n<li>Assign a report</li>\n<li>Unassign a report</li>\n<li>Set an award</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.800000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-actions\"\n        title=\"report-actions\"\n        src=\"/static/7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35/0b533/report-actions-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35/fac75/report-actions-1.png 125w,\n/static/7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35/63868/report-actions-1.png 250w,\n/static/7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35/0b533/report-actions-1.png 500w,\n/static/7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35/1d69c/report-actions-1.png 750w,\n/static/7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35/00d43/report-actions-1.png 1000w,\n/static/7d7d8c0b6136640f7d10fb40afac9c35/c8ad9/report-actions-1.png 1564w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"add-a-comment\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#add-a-comment\" aria-label=\"add a comment permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Add a Comment</h3>\n<p>You can dialogue with hackers or team members or make notes about the report through adding comments.</p>\n<p>To add a comment:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Make sure the action picker is set to <strong>Add comment</strong>.</li>\n<li>Select who you would like to make the comment visible to. You can select from these options:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Team only</td>\n<td>Only the members of your program will be able to view the comment.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>All participants</td>\n<td>All participants of the report will be able to view the comment.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<blockquote>\n<p><i>Note: When you're adding a comment to your internal team only, the comment box will turn red.</i></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-actions-2\"\n        title=\"report-actions-2\"\n        src=\"/static/31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982/0b533/report-action-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982/fac75/report-action-2.png 125w,\n/static/31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982/63868/report-action-2.png 250w,\n/static/31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982/0b533/report-action-2.png 500w,\n/static/31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982/1d69c/report-action-2.png 750w,\n/static/31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982/00d43/report-action-2.png 1000w,\n/static/31a61c56336ad2bd57cb25a621a82982/df438/report-action-2.png 1556w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"close-a-report\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#close-a-report\" aria-label=\"close a report permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Close a Report</h3>\n<p>You can close a report to mark that it's either:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Resolved</li>\n<li>Informative</li>\n<li>Not Applicable</li>\n<li>Duplicate</li>\n<li>Spam</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To close a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Select <strong>Close report</strong> in the action picker.</li>\n<li>Select the status of the report in the <strong>Select status</strong> action picker.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Close report</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.800000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-action-3\"\n        title=\"report-action-3\"\n        src=\"/static/00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9/0b533/report-actions-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9/fac75/report-actions-3.png 125w,\n/static/00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9/63868/report-actions-3.png 250w,\n/static/00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9/0b533/report-actions-3.png 500w,\n/static/00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9/1d69c/report-actions-3.png 750w,\n/static/00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9/00d43/report-actions-3.png 1000w,\n/static/00a5645aa50fa3fd94e7842a8463fcc9/9f9a4/report-actions-3.png 1560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong><em>Note:</em></strong> <em>Reports that have gone through <a href=\"human-augmented-signal.html\">Human-Augmented Signal</a> can be reopened by the hacker if closed</em></p>\n<h3 id=\"change-the-state\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#change-the-state\" aria-label=\"change the state permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the State</h3>\n<p>You can change the state of a report to be marked as either <em>triaged</em> or <em>new</em>. This'll help you keep track of what state your report is in.</p>\n<p>To change the state of a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Change the action picker from <strong>Add comment</strong> to <strong>Change state</strong> from the drop-down.  </li>\n<li>Select the state of the report. You can choose from:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Triaged</td>\n<td>The report has passed the initial validation and is pending resolution. You can briefly describe the next steps in the comments section such as further investigation, escalation, engineer preparing a fix. *(Optional) When you select triage, you can enter the reference ID to your integration in the <strong>Reference ID</strong> field.*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>New</td>\n<td>The report is pending triage and validation.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click <strong>Change state</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-action-5\"\n        title=\"report-action-5\"\n        src=\"/static/cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc/0b533/report-action-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc/fac75/report-action-5.png 125w,\n/static/cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc/63868/report-action-5.png 250w,\n/static/cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc/0b533/report-action-5.png 500w,\n/static/cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc/1d69c/report-action-5.png 750w,\n/static/cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc/00d43/report-action-5.png 1000w,\n/static/cff11347191b812f753d48693c7265fc/df438/report-action-5.png 1556w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"assign-a-report\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#assign-a-report\" aria-label=\"assign a report permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Assign a Report</h3>\n<p>You can assign reports to individual members or groups in your program to evaluate and take action on a report.</p>\n<p>To assign a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Change the action picker from <strong>Add comment</strong> to <strong>Assign report</strong> from the drop-down.  </li>\n<li>Enter the username of the assignee or the group.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Assign report</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"assign report\"\n        title=\"assign report\"\n        src=\"/static/db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa/0b533/assign-report.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa/fac75/assign-report.png 125w,\n/static/db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa/63868/assign-report.png 250w,\n/static/db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa/0b533/assign-report.png 500w,\n/static/db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa/1d69c/assign-report.png 750w,\n/static/db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa/00d43/assign-report.png 1000w,\n/static/db2b0eeea376219917680ba1af6cecaa/61946/assign-report.png 1546w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"unassign-a-report\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#unassign-a-report\" aria-label=\"unassign a report permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Unassign a Report</h3>\n<p>Once a report has been assigned, you can elect to unassign a report.</p>\n<p>To unassign a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the assigned report in your inbox.</li>\n<li>Change the action picker from <strong>Add comment</strong> to <strong>Assign report</strong> from the drop-down.</li>\n<li>Click <b>Unassign report</b>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>No one will be assigned to the report. You can reassign the report by following the steps in the <b>Assign a Report</b> section.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.800000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"unassign report\"\n        title=\"unassign report\"\n        src=\"/static/152db815102fda280b16f5fa88473b4c/0b533/unassign-report.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/152db815102fda280b16f5fa88473b4c/fac75/unassign-report.png 125w,\n/static/152db815102fda280b16f5fa88473b4c/63868/unassign-report.png 250w,\n/static/152db815102fda280b16f5fa88473b4c/0b533/unassign-report.png 500w,\n/static/152db815102fda280b16f5fa88473b4c/1d69c/unassign-report.png 750w,\n/static/152db815102fda280b16f5fa88473b4c/00d43/unassign-report.png 1000w,\n/static/152db815102fda280b16f5fa88473b4c/67a79/unassign-report.png 1408w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"set-an-award\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#set-an-award\" aria-label=\"set an award permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Set an Award</h3>\n<p>You can mark that you've rewarded a hacker with swag or a monetary amount through setting awards.</p>\n<p>To set an award to a hacker for the report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report above the comment box.</li>\n<li>Change the action picker from <strong>Add comment</strong> to <strong>Set award</strong> from the drop-down.  </li>\n<li>Select the type of award you want to reward the hacker with. You can choose from these options:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Amount</td>\n<td>Mark that you've rewarded the hacker with a specific dollar amount for the vulnerability.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>None ( ineligible)</td>\n<td>The report is ineligible for a bounty. It's best to explain the reasons to hackers in the comments section, why the report is ineligible.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Suggest amount</td>\n<td>Suggest a bounty amount to award the hacker. Only internal members of your program will be able to view your bounty suggestion.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Swag</td>\n<td>Mark that you've rewarded the hacker with swag.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click <strong>Set award</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.599999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-action-4\"\n        title=\"report-action-4\"\n        src=\"/static/37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11/0b533/report-action-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11/fac75/report-action-4.png 125w,\n/static/37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11/63868/report-action-4.png 250w,\n/static/37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11/0b533/report-action-4.png 500w,\n/static/37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11/1d69c/report-action-4.png 750w,\n/static/37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11/00d43/report-action-4.png 1000w,\n/static/37dba030ae3d6fba384506f77c20ae11/64639/report-action-4.png 1568w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/report-actions.html","id":"programs/report-actions","title":"Report Actions","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Add a Comment"},{"value":"Close a Report"},{"value":"Change the State"},{"value":"Assign a Report"},{"value":"Unassign a Report"},{"value":"Set an Award"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}